results.name: Fourth power of lower triangular matrix of A056857 (successive equalities in set partitions of n).
comment: First column gives A078944. Row sums are given by A078945.
formula: Exponential function of 4*Pascal's triangle (taken as a lower triangular matrix) divided by e^4: [A078939] = (1/e^4)*exp(4*[A007318]) = [A056857]^4.
results.author: _Paul D. Hanna_, Dec 18 2002
